Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm Jinno Megumi,\NIzumi Sagiri-chan's classmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.09,0:00:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri's classmate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm the class representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, are you Izumi-san's older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, you're not related to her by blood, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And you live all alone\Nwith your younger sister. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We do have a guardian,\Nwho is almost never home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's see, it was Jinno-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just call me Megumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, Megumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to get along with you too, Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you can't call me Megumin, then please\Ncall me just Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Well then, nice to meet you, Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There can't be any boys who don't fall in love\Nwith me at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you one of those who love boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.91,0:01:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.66,0:01:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I couldn't fall in love that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You fool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.04,0:01:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Every day, I wash the panties of my younger sister,\Na much more beautiful girl than you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I'd fall for any woman\Nat first sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.47,0:01:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't react to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,then your penis really is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, that's ri—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What... did you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,say {\i1}penis{\i0} or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did! Is something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Penises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Love!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.12,0:01:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes! Girls my age all love penises!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'm sure your younger sister loves penises, too.\N- Wh-What has happened to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That just can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That was a joke. Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why the hell did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I came here to get Izumi Sagiri-san\Nto go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is such a cute calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the calendar for a novel I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not Izumi-san, but you, Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you one of those otaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stab!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.75,0:04:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm also a big otaku as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've always been reading a lot of manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, that's unusual.\NWhat kind of things do you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love stuff like OnePi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.10,0:04:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I see. I love that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because it's a "super-popular" title\Nthat everyone knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is Izumi-san's room on the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your classmate's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's rather angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, Izumi here. Who may this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you calling me\Nwhile you're still in the house?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the only way I could speak to you\Nwithout opening the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's fine. But how did you know my number?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-Anyway, Nii-san,\Nwh-what's the meaning of this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, the class rep for your class\Nis here at our place right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why did you let her inside our house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, maybe you would\Ncome out of the room because of thi—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way! I won't, won't, won't!\NI said I won't, so I won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chase her out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe by phone,\Nyou can talk to your classmate—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I can't chase her out immediately,\Nso I'll just listen to what she has to say. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, h-hold on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that class rep a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll give you orders every so often,\Nso make sure she doesn't notice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you went up to call her down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. I did call out to her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She just won't leave her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How's that! There's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Don't say that so arrogantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}To think she won't leave her room....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Onii-san, do you think it's okay\Nto stay this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Of course I don't think it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For the past year, I've been doing my best\Nin my own way so she'll come out of her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, your objective is the same as mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Well, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, Onii-san, form an alliance with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll call it the\N"Alliance to Drag Izumi-chan out of Her Room"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,An alliance, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please sit next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? Onii-san, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your face is all red. So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calling you "Onii-san"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.14,0:07:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with her? So irritating.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're being all spoony\Nand stuff! You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-In the first place,\Nwhy do you want Sagiri to go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love making new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After entering middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I immediately became friends\Nwith everyone in the same grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E-Everyone!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I realized I hadn't\Nbecome friends with Izumi-chan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And so, I'm totally passionate about\Ngetting Izumi-chan to come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really hate this type.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hypocrite forcing their kindness\Nonto others. Go home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And? What are you specifically going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san, do you know exactly what Izumi-chan\Nis doing, all cooped up in her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The typical case is someone plinking around\Nforever on the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If so, there's a secret plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Secret plan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please cancel your internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, let's call your provider right now,\Nand cut off the root of all evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're not human!\NDo you think you're God or something!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-When did this story get so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All things considered, that's way too rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you have friends, you don't need\Nthe internet or computers and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or rather, it's kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't have friends, isn't it meaningless\Nto have just the internet on hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, you have no friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Well, there's all sorts of stuff you can do\Nif you have a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't it a lot more fun\Nto be chatting with friends at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More like, that voice just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's fine. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.67,0:09:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Izumi-chan, you're listening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nii-san, bluff your way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't ask for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- She found out, so...\N- Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-chan, if you end the conversation\Nright now, you might regret it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is this wench saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rub, rub! Rub, rub! Hehe, Onii-san smells nice!\N- H-Hey, what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san, your heart is finally racing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Stop th—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san, have you ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,kissed anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-chan, nice to meet you! I'm Megumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here you go. She hung up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, can I ask a few questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.17,0:10:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of a girl is Izumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of a girl? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's tremendously beautiful\Nand cute in appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She hung up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At first glance, she's expressionless,\Nand quiet. But she's truly a lovely maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you talk to her, her facial expression\Nchanges often, and she's really charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you laughing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing! And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's a tremendously good artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh? What kind of art?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- She's really good at lewd art!\N- Lewd art?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah. Tremendously wonderful lewd art!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}C-Can it be that Izumi-chan\Nis a perverted girl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Erotic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, she's a first year in middle school,\Nbut quite the panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...are worn!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...are drawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,G-Geez. I had totally thought Izumi-chan\Nand Onii-san were in a really weird relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop with the impossible misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just because we live together doesn't mean\Nbrother and sister have a romantic relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you quiet there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No, nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then, one last question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How do you want your younger sister to end up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean, how?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you really serious\Nabout making her go to school?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, it's like you're protecting\Nyour younger sister from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}- You could say that I'm not, come to think.\N- What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want Sagiri to come out of her room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If she stayed home,\Nshe'll never have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Friends, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She does have friends, or rather,\Nlots of people who think dearly of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.57,DefaultC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(187.267,219.111)}"When you speak of dreams,\Nyou should laugh!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, even if she's not going to school,\Nor even if she doesn't leave her room,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My younger sister is my pride and joy.\NI'm proud of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's what you think about Izumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh no, I'll be coming again.\NI haven't given up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll come up with a plan that'll make\NIzumi-chan volunteer to go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, my regards\Nfor the days to come, Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, I heard a strange sound earlier,\Nbut are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.25,0:13:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I guess she won't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Izumi-chan,\Nyou sure are loved by your brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the project proposals you sent us\Nare no good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were all crap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bring some new ones\Nbefore the meeting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- See you.\N- H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Balse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri. I'll leave your meal here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Replenish snacks soon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.34,EpNum,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(364.817,276.889)}Adachi Fourth Public High School
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- See you!\N- Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yo! You look somewhat tired there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was writing up a plot until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm heading to a meeting for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I still have a bit of time,\Nso I'll drop by Takasago Books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please buy a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.57,LeftSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\frz7.309\pos(265,168.444)}Tomoe's Recommendation Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing less from Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a great lineup here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder if my books are selling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Silverwolf of Reincarnation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All volumes are still in stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- All right.\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, the author is promoting his own work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're interfering with my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Put them back in the shelves they were in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At the least, as a friend, can't you put them\Nin the recommendation shelf?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:15:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Currently, I'm displaying Yamada Elf-sensei's\Nautographed books with the cover showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll sign my books too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I won't be able to return them if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's getting an anime version.\NBut it really is an interesting series.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mune-kun, if you want your stuff\Nlined up on my recommendation shelf,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,write some super-interesting novel\Nthat strikes chords in readers' hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Damn! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That aside, can I get the autographed book\Nby Yamada Elf-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks, as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why isn't it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I, as an Oricon #1 author, am saying so!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So? Why do you think I'd do something\Nthat would benefit another company?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kagurazaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As a special favor,\NI'll write my next series for your company!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? No thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? I couldn't hear you clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am an Oricon #1 author!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I am the prettiest\Nand best light-novel author in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I'm saying I'll wear the tainted name of\Ntraitor to write for this publishing company!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Such an exceptional condition won't ever come\Nagain for all eternity if you miss it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you go home soon, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei, I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sheesh, you don't have to be hiding over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm talking to her right now.\NPlease don't butt in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, what's the situation here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More like, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is Izumi Masamune-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, this is Yamada Elf-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Y- Yamada Elf-sensei?\N- Izumi Masamune?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sh-She's such a young girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So there were authors this young\Nother than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, what is Yamada Elf-sensei\Ndoing in our editorial office?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why, thank you for asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's because Eromanga-sensei\Nwill be drawing illustrations for my next title!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm head over heels in love\Nwith Eromanga-sensei's illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want that lewd paintbrush to draw\Nthe best, fully naked human in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Add my literary talent to that,\Nand without a doubt, it's a decisive advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}The "ultimate light-novel" that nobody\Nhas ever seen before will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}No, Eromanga-sensei is paired up with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Instead of drawing illustrations for\Na lowly author who isn't even on the rankings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}working together with me,\Na super-popular author, has got to be better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sales numbers are justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just you wait. I'll pile my books\Non top of yours at the bookstore again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Stop that. My books will be tainted if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And did you just say "again"?\NYou really are the scum of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yamada-sensei. I've said this many times,\Nbut the decision is up to Eromanga-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I've been telling you\Nthat Eromanga-sensei hasn't replied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want you to do some convincing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you know who I,\Nan Oricon #1 author, exactly am!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think your popularity is merely a fluke.\NHow about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What was that? Correct yourself, stupid editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You will bow down before my literary talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Literary talent? Yamada-sensei,\Nyour novels are often dissed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,in curator websites,\Nclaiming you write terrible sentences.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's wrong! I'm writing in a way\Nthat's easy to understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really! You don't understand anything!\NSuch an incompetent editor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Look here, remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All light-novel authors\Nother than me are outdated scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And nowadays, my sentences,\Nthat are easy to read and understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is paving the new path\Nfor the world of light-novels!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.02,0:19:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In other words,\NI am the savior of the light-novel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No! I am light-novel itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Yeah, yeah. See you later, Light-novel-chan.\N- H-Hey, what...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you don't go home soon, I'll file\Na complaint to the editor in charge of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What, th-that's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. 10, 9, 8, 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'll go home for today! But, just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm going to go tattle\Nto all my cute servants on Twitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, Izumi-sensei.\NThis is turning into a bad situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What that troublesome author was saying\Nhad a pretty good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Instead of a no-name like me,\Na popular author like Yamada Elf is better....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So? What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ugh, oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why isn't this elevator coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.22,0:20:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll definitely write a novel\Nthat's more interesting than hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So don't abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you being rowdy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Abandon and all that...\NWhat's that about? Did you have a nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-No, i-it's nothing. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, you opened the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:49.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well... Um, uh... Umm....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, that's the important part!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:21:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san... Um...\NDid you hear anything from that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That girl? You mean Megumi?\NWhat do you mean by anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, did you buy the snacks\Nthat I asked for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I bought you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Konbu and Rakugan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is a good time, so I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, the snacks you buy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,are like offerings for Buddhist altars,\Nand not all that tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't buy snacks of this kind anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:42.22,OP_Romaji,NTP,0,0,0,,That, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll wash my own underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So please don't touch them ever again.
